y\nto imply a 2-quark nature for $a_0(1450)$ and a four-quark assignment for\n$a_0(980)$. The penguin-dominated modes $a_0(980)K$ and $a_0(1450)K$ receive\ndominant weak annihilation contributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2005 18:44:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 8 Oct 2005 07:44:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2005 05:57:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
