s power law decay in time. The model predicts\nthat social interaction helps to prevent aversion, and that products are viewed\nmore positively when their consumption rate is higher.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2005 15:27:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2005 07:57:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
